name: Rayno Vaca
Lore: 'Coruscant taxi driver who barely makes enough money to get by. Will try any trick in the book to get an extra credit from his customer.',
Text: 'Your characters may move from here using their landspeed for free. During your control phase, may place Vaca in Used Pile to take Lana Dobreed into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
